There are four possible alignments: "RIGHT_LEFT" (default), "LEFT_RIGHT", "LEFT_LEFT", and "RIGHT_RIGHT". It is the packing format LAPACK uses. cuSPARSE uses "LEFT_RIGHT", which is the opposite alignment.
